\c 20
\s Umkhuleko wokucela ukunqoba
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. Isihlabelelo sikaDavida
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* ikuphendule osukwini lokuhlupheka; ibizo likaNkulunkulu kaJakobe likuvikele.
\v 2 Kayikuthumele usizo oluvela endaweni engcwele\x + 2 Lan. 20.8. Hlab. 73.17. 74.7.\x*, ikusekele iseZiyoni\x + Hlab. 128.5.\x*.
\v 3 Kayikhumbule yonke iminikelo yakho, njalo yemukele umnikelo wakho wokutshiswa. \w Sela\w**.
\v 4 Ikunike njengokwenhliziyo yakho, njalo igcwalise icebo lakho lonke\x + Hlab. 21.2.\x*.
\v 5 Simemeze ngentokozo esindisweni lwakho\x + Hlab. 9.14.\x*, lebizweni likaNkulunkulu wethu siphakamise iziboniso\x + Eks. 17.15. Hlab. 60.4.\x*! IN\nd kosi\nd* igcwalise konke ukucela kwakho\x + Hlab. 21.2.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Sengisazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* isindisa ogcotshiweyo wayo\x + Hlab. 18.50. Hlab. 2.2.\x*; izamphendula isemazulwini ayo angcwele ngamandla asindisayo esandla sayo sokunene.
\v 7 Abanye \add bathembela\add* enqoleni, labanye emabhizeni, kodwa thina sizakhumbula ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu\x + Isa. 31.1. 36.9. Hlab. 33.17.\x*.
\v 8 Bona bakhothanyisiwe bawa, kodwa thina sisukumile simi\x + Hlab. 146.9. 147.6.\x*.
\v 9 Jehova, sindisa; inkosi isiphendule osukwini lokukhala kwethu.